  <h1>{guide.title}</h1>
  <p class="lead">A water filter is only as good as its maintenance. A neglected filter does not just stop working — it can become a breeding ground for bacteria and actually make your water worse. This guide covers replacement schedules, warning signs of filter failure, cleaning techniques, and maintenance best practices for every filter type we review.</p>

